    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. Mechanically, it runs smoothly with consistent maintenance records, and all major systems are functioning as they should. The exterior retains a nice finish, though you will find some minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only light wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. It is a dependable, high-quality vehicle that offers a great balance of reliability and value for its next owner.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
